  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p&gt;The proposed development, in the absence of a daylight and sunlight report and annotated plans the proposal fails to demonstrate sufficient levels of light into habitable rooms,&amp;nbsp; contrary to part MA.2(2)(f) of Class MA, Part 3, Schedule 2 of the Town and Country Planning (General Permitted Development) (England) Order 2015 (as amended).&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;",
    "&lt;p&gt;The proposed change of use is contrary to MA.1(1)(b) as the applicant has failed to demonstrate the property has been vacant for the previous 2 years and is contrary to Class MA of Part 3 of Schedule 2 of the Town and Country Planning (General Permitted Development) (England) Order 2015 (as amended).&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;",
    "&lt;p&gt;The proposed development, in the absence of a legal agreement to secure car-free housing,&amp;nbsp; and lack of adequate information to determine if sufficient cycle parking can be provided, fails to promote sustainable modes of transport and would contribute to air pollution and congestion in the surrounding area,&amp;nbsp; contrary to part MA.2(2)(a) of Class MA, Part 3, Schedule 2 of the Town and Country Planning (General Permitted Development) (England) Order 2015 (as amended).&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;"
  ],
